project_descr: Project Initiation Plan for the Localization of the Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs).

outputs.output_descr:
1. Production of Audio Visual and Print materials (including flags, pens, folders, bookmarks, posters, brochures) 
2. Procurement of Equipment (tripod, camera, back up cleaning kit, mobile phone, projector, microphone)
3. Production of Videos on SDGs implementation and success stories to date
4. Dissemination of educational and awareness materials
SDGs are incorporated into Region 9 Plan of Action for Regional Development (PARD)

1. Mainstreaming of SDGs across the following thematic areas: 
-	Constitutional Reform 
-	Promotion of Social Cohesion 
-	Gender Parity
-	Awareness on NCDs
-	Promotion of Human Rights 
-	Promotion of Business Sector 
-	Support for MAPS mission
-	Support for Peace and Development
